name: Sri Venkateswara Garments
overview:
Sri Venkateswara Garments started its business operations in the year 1978 at Bengaluru, Karnataka in India.

Infrastructure: Our sprawling infrastructure spreads across acres of land. To carry out all our activities in a streamlined manner, we have sectioned our infrastructure into varied departments.

Our Quality Assurance: Ever since our establishment, we follow an efficient quality control that revolves across varied stages of production and dispatch.

Our Team: Capable and diligent team forms the basis of our success and growth. Our team comprises talented pool of professionals that make effective utilization of varied stitching, sewing and cutting machines to offer superior quality Uniforms and Garments.

Why Us: With more than 3 decades of market presence, we have emerged as one of the prominent names involved in manufacturing and supplying exclusive range of Garments and Uniforms.

OUR PRODUCT RANGE: School Uniforms School Skirts School T-Shirts Student Lab Coats School Socks School Belts School Ties
